  "detailed_description": "Do you have the guts to face the ultimate zombie nightmare? <br>Do you have the skills to survive the most brutal top-down zombie shooter ever?<br><br>In this game, you will face endless waves of zombies, each more vicious and hungry than the last. You will have to use your skills, tactics, and reflexes to stay alive and fight your way to the exit. <br>You have a huge arsenal of weapons at your disposal, from axes and machetes to flamethrowers and rocket launchers. You can slash, burn, blast, and explode your enemies with over 20 types of weapons, each with its own unique features and upgrades.<br><br>You have allies, who will help you in your mission. <br>But there is a catch. One bite, and your ally will turn into a zombie.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761550/extras/578f63d0366e5bcb2c026b0c85ac845a.poster.avif?t=1723505944\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761550/extras/578f63d0366e5bcb2c026b0c85ac845a.webm?t=1723505944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761550/extras/578f63d0366e5bcb2c026b0c85ac845a.mp4?t=1723505944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Do you have the guts to face the ultimate zombie nightmare? <br>Do you have the skills to survive the most brutal top-down zombie shooter ever?<br><br>In this game, you will face endless waves of zombies, each more vicious and hungry than the last. You will have to use your skills, tactics, and reflexes to stay alive and fight your way to the exit. <br>You have a huge arsenal of weapons at your disposal, from axes and machetes to flamethrowers and rocket launchers. You can slash, burn, blast, and explode your enemies with over 20 types of weapons, each with its own unique features and upgrades.<br><br>You have allies, who will help you in your mission. <br>But there is a catch. One bite, and your ally will turn into a zombie.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761550/extras/578f63d0366e5bcb2c026b0c85ac845a.poster.avif?t=1723505944\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761550/extras/578f63d0366e5bcb2c026b0c85ac845a.webm?t=1723505944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761550/extras/578f63d0366e5bcb2c026b0c85ac845a.mp4?t=1723505944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
